## Matriz Modulith (`allowedDependencies`)

| Módulo | Depende de |
|--------|------------|
| `shared-kernel` | — |
| `domain-identity` | `shared::*` |
| `domain-authorize` | `shared::*`, `identity::usuarios`, `identity::grupos`, `identity::infra-attributes` |
| `domain-backoffice` | `shared::*`, `identity::*` (usuarios, grupos, roles), `authorize::*`, `notification::events` |
| `domain-notification` | `shared::*` |
| `domain-location` | `shared::*` |
| `domain-security` | `shared::*`, `authorize::authorize-ports`, `authorize::domain`, `plataformadmin::usuarios`, `plataformadmin::usuarios-domain`, `identity::usuarios` |

Admin consome eventos de notification apenas via pacote `notification::events`.

## Eventos entre módulos

```
UsuarioSistemaCriadoEvent (plataformadmin)
  → UsuarioSistemaListeners (plataformadmin)
  → NotificacaoBoasVindasEvent (notification::events)
  → NotificacaoEventListeners (notification)
```

Troca de senha (`authorize`) publica `NotificacaoTrocaSenhaEvent`. Preferir listeners a chamadas diretas service-to-service para supporting domains.

